<paragraph id="007606418F43FECD48A751B0FB85F941" blockId="269.[151,1436,151,2035]" box="[151,1056,1691,1714]" pageId="269" pageNumber="270">
Dryinus hainanensis Olmi 1987a: 424; He &amp; Xu 2002: 262; Xu et al. 
<quantity id="C731ABA48F43FECD4B6C51B7FC3FF941" box="[860,922,1691,1713]" metricMagnitude="0" metricUnit="kg" metricValue="2.011" pageId="269" pageNumber="270" unit="g" value="2011.0">2011g</quantity>
